The preliminary determination is

284
00:13:33,200 --> 00:13:33,770
suicide.

285
00:13:38,120 --> 00:13:40,000
Leilei couldn't have committed suicide.

286
00:13:40,000 --> 00:13:41,670
She couldn't have.

287
00:13:41,950 --> 00:13:44,690
She would never leave her parents behind.

288
00:13:45,480 --> 00:13:46,910
Besides, she was about to get married.

289
00:13:46,910 --> 00:13:47,310
She...

290
00:13:48,270 --> 00:13:49,480
Everything was going well for her.

291
00:13:49,480 --> 00:13:51,510
She had no reason to do this.

292
00:13:53,080 --> 00:13:53,720
Ms. Yan.

293
00:13:54,320 --> 00:13:56,480
You mentioned
she was about to get married?

294
00:13:56,480 --> 00:13:57,830
Who's her fiance?

295
00:14:01,600 --> 00:14:02,600
His name is Xia Yi.

296
00:14:03,840 --> 00:14:04,640
The two of them

297
00:14:05,670 --> 00:14:08,120
met at a bank reception.

298
00:14:09,900 --> 00:14:12,160
They've always had a good relationship.

299
00:14:13,840 --> 00:14:15,900
Do you have his contact information?

300
00:14:16,390 --> 00:14:17,440
No, I don't.

301
00:14:18,840 --> 00:14:20,640
Leilei must have it on her phone.

302
00:14:25,510 --> 00:14:26,030
Ms. Yan,

303
00:14:26,350 --> 00:14:28,390
[Dad, Mom. I'm sorry. I'm sorry.]

304
00:14:27,040 --> 00:14:28,100
please take a look.

305
00:14:28,510 --> 00:14:30,510
Is this Jian Leilei's handwriting?

306
00:14:34,390 --> 00:14:34,840
Dad,

307
00:14:36,840 --> 00:14:37,200
Mom.

308
00:14:39,630 --> 00:14:40,270
I'm sorry.

309
00:14:40,960 --> 00:14:42,270
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

310
00:14:44,910 --> 00:14:46,790
I've made a terrible mistake

311
00:14:48,550 --> 00:14:50,810
that I can't make up for in this lifetime.

312
00:14:51,240 --> 00:14:53,840
I owe you too much.

313
00:14:54,200 --> 00:14:55,930
I'll repay you in the next life.

314
00:14:57,200 --> 00:14:58,430
I'm sorry, Jiale.

315
00:14:58,630 --> 00:15:00,630
I can't be there to watch you grow up.

316
00:15:00,960 --> 00:15:02,240
I will always love you.

317
00:15:03,960 --> 00:15:04,910
I'm sorry, Ling.

318
00:15:05,960 --> 00:15:09,290
In our next life, I promise
we'll travel the world together.

319
00:15:09,750 --> 00:15:10,350
Remember,

320
00:15:11,080 --> 00:15:12,420
you must live well

321
00:15:12,750 --> 00:15:13,440
for me...

322
00:15:14,120 --> 00:15:15,440
For my sake.

323
00:15:16,200 --> 00:15:17,390
You promised me.

324
00:15:29,240 --> 00:15:29,600
Here.

325
00:15:34,030 --> 00:15:35,270
Where's our Leilei?

326
00:15:35,300 --> 00:15:37,000
-This way.
-Where's our Leilei?

327
00:15:37,000 --> 00:15:37,360
Come with me.

328
00:15:37,120 --> 00:15:43,300
[Police]

329
00:15:39,510 --> 00:15:40,570
Careful. Careful.

330
00:15:43,430 --> 00:15:46,380
[Emergency Department Lobby]
[Emergency Exam Room]

331
00:15:46,550 --> 00:15:47,430
Mrs. Feng.

332
00:15:47,910 --> 00:15:48,910
I have to trouble you again

333
00:15:48,910 --> 00:15:51,080
to go check on Li Changning for me today.

334
00:15:51,080 --> 00:15:53,030
I've got something urgent to handle

335
00:15:53,030 --> 00:15:54,100
and can't get away.

336
00:15:55,720 --> 00:15:56,920
It's not about my son.

337
00:15:56,960 --> 00:15:58,160
It's something else.

338
00:15:59,030 --> 00:16:02,400
[Emergency]

339
00:15:59,480 --> 00:16:00,510
Okay, I understand.

340
00:16:00,510 --> 00:16:01,110
Thank you.

341
00:16:09,790 --> 00:16:10,440
Uncle,

342
00:16:11,680 --> 00:16:12,810
how is Auntie doing?

343
00:16:13,520 --> 00:16:14,380
A bit better.

344
00:16:15,750 --> 00:16:16,430
Yan Ling,

345
00:16:17,440 --> 00:16:18,660
could you please

346
00:16:18,810 --> 00:16:20,270
take me to Leilei's place?

347
00:16:20,780 --> 00:16:22,760
I want to get a pair of shoes for her.

348
00:16:27,410 --> 00:16:28,270
No problem.

349
00:16:32,620 --> 00:16:33,420
Sorry.

350
00:16:33,840 --> 00:16:36,550
The number you have dialed
is temporarily unavailable.

351
00:16:36,550 --> 00:16:37,900
Please try again later.

352
00:16:39,080 --> 00:16:40,480
Leilei mentioned before

353
00:16:41,510 --> 00:16:43,030
that when Xia Yi's on a mission,

354
00:16:43,030 --> 00:16:44,690
his phone often has no signal.

355
00:16:45,060 --> 00:16:46,200
Once he sees it,

356
00:16:46,360 --> 00:16:47,530
he will call back.

357
00:16:48,510 --> 00:16:50,110
She was doing so well.

358
00:16:51,630 --> 00:16:52,960
How could she suddenly

359
00:16:54,080 --> 00:16:55,440
lose hope like that?

360
00:17:16,490 --> 00:17:16,920
[To Ling]

361
00:17:16,920 --> 00:17:19,930
[Bank Card Number] [Password]
[WeChat Account] [Password]

362
00:17:19,950 --> 00:17:23,300
[Weibo Account] [Password]
[Alipay Account] [Password]

363
00:17:27,869 --> 00:17:30,080
[Personal Insurance Application Form]

364
00:17:41,860 --> 00:17:46,170
[Household Register]

365
00:17:48,000 --> 00:17:49,200
Why did you do this?

366
00:17:51,440 --> 00:17:53,440
Why did you do this...

367
00:17:57,310 --> 00:17:58,840
I'll go get some toiletries

368
00:17:58,880 --> 00:18:00,000
for you and Auntie.

369
00:18:34,130 --> 00:18:37,220
[Police]

370
00:18:35,280 --> 00:18:35,920
It's freezing outside.

371
00:18:35,920 --> 00:18:37,450
Wouldn't it be better to
enjoy some hotpot?

372
00:18:37,450 --> 00:18:38,200
You prefer to come here instead, huh?

373
00:18:38,040 --> 00:18:40,820
[Reception Area]

374
00:18:38,350 --> 00:18:39,080
Move faster!

375
00:18:39,480 --> 00:18:40,080
Chubby Li,

376
00:18:40,480 --> 00:18:41,550
help me take a statement.

377
00:18:41,550 --> 00:18:43,070
I don't have time, bro.

378
00:18:43,070 --> 00:18:44,400
I haven't even finished the briefing
for the higher-ups

379
00:18:44,400 --> 00:18:46,750
about that suicide case
I'm the liaison for.

380
00:18:46,750 --> 00:18:48,210
Look at all this fat on you.

381
00:18:48,400 --> 00:18:49,680
If you don't get more active,

382
00:18:49,680 --> 00:18:51,070
how will you pass the physical test?

383
00:18:51,070 --> 00:18:53,950
Master, I'm just office staff.
I don't need to go on patrol.

384
00:18:53,950 --> 00:18:55,310
Running into that suicide case yesterday

385
00:18:55,310 --> 00:18:56,290
was purely accidental.

386
00:18:55,900 --> 00:18:57,140
[General Services Window]

387
00:18:56,550 --> 00:18:57,080
Officer.

388
00:18:57,270 --> 00:18:57,790
Report!

389
00:18:58,160 --> 00:18:58,620
Report!

390
00:18:58,880 --> 00:18:59,790
We're here to file a report.

391
00:18:59,790 --> 00:19:00,590
We're here to file a report.

392
00:19:00,590 --> 00:19:01,070
Here's the thing.

393
00:19:01,070 --> 00:19:03,000
I'm from the Binjiang Branch
of Ninghai Commercial Bank,

394
00:19:03,000 --> 00:19:04,110
Jian Leilei's direct supervisor.

395
00:19:04,110 --> 00:19:04,960
My surname is Zhang.

396
00:19:04,960 --> 00:19:05,830
This afternoon,

397
00:19:05,830 --> 00:19:07,590
the police informed us
that something happened to Jian Leilei.

398
00:19:07,590 --> 00:19:08,050
Yes.

399
00:19:08,270 --> 00:19:09,270
She was our VIP client.

400
00:19:09,270 --> 00:19:10,310
Let me take it from here.

401
00:19:10,310 --> 00:19:11,440
That Jian Leilei

402
00:19:11,440 --> 00:19:13,270
had always been
my personal financial advisor.

403
00:19:13,270 --> 00:19:13,720
She had

404
00:19:13,720 --> 00:19:14,240
been managing

405
00:19:14,240 --> 00:19:15,880
some of my liquid funds here in China.

406
00:19:15,880 --> 00:19:17,480
I just returned from abroad.

407
00:19:17,590 --> 00:19:18,030
I had

408
00:19:18,030 --> 00:19:19,640
an appointment at the bank this morning

409
00:19:19,640 --> 00:19:21,160
with her and Manager Zhang

410
00:19:21,310 --> 00:19:23,390
to talk about a new financial plan,

411
00:19:23,590 --> 00:19:24,850
but she didn't show up.

412
00:19:26,160 --> 00:19:27,720
I checked my account, and it was shocking—

413
00:19:27,720 --> 00:19:28,920
she stole 1.8 million yuan

414
00:19:28,920 --> 00:19:30,780
from my account!

415
00:19:31,200 --> 00:19:31,800
That much?

416
00:19:56,110 --> 00:19:57,440
What's wrong, Yan Ling?

417
00:20:00,000 --> 00:20:00,860
Before, Leilei

418
00:20:01,400 --> 00:20:03,110
was worried you and Auntie
would be upset,

419
00:20:03,110 --> 00:20:04,910
so she probably didn't tell you.

420
00:20:06,110 --> 00:20:07,200
Actually, she and Xia Yi

421
00:20:07,200 --> 00:20:09,400
had been living together for some time.

422
00:20:09,720 --> 00:20:11,120
But now, there's no trace

423
00:20:11,720 --> 00:20:13,640
of Xia Yi's presence here at all.

424
00:20:21,160 --> 00:20:21,640
Master.

425
00:20:22,030 --> 00:20:24,160
We've obtained
Jian Leilei's bank statements

426
00:20:24,160 --> 00:20:26,030
and tracked the money trail in detail.

427
00:20:26,030 --> 00:20:27,640
We found that
starting about two months ago,

428
00:20:27,640 --> 00:20:29,830
she had been frequently
operating client accounts.

429
00:20:29,830 --> 00:20:31,550
At first, she would transfer money
to her own card

430
00:20:31,550 --> 00:20:32,880
and return it after a while.

431
00:20:32,880 --> 00:20:34,960
Later, money only went in
but never came out again.

432
00:20:34,960 --> 00:20:37,480
In total, she misappropriated about

433
00:20:38,070 --> 00:20:39,070
1.8 million yuan.

434
00:20:40,720 --> 00:20:42,550
She used it all
to buy a type of cryptocurrency.

435
00:20:42,550 --> 00:20:44,110
She even used triple leverage.

436
00:20:44,110 --> 00:20:45,040
Until recently,

437
00:20:45,190 --> 00:20:47,200
when this cryptocurrency
suddenly crashed in value,

438
00:20:47,200 --> 00:20:49,460
Jian Leilei basically lost everything.

439
00:20:50,830 --> 00:20:52,550
Suspected of misappropriating funds?

440
00:20:52,550 --> 00:20:53,210
And

441
00:20:53,720 --> 00:20:55,000
the amount is substantial.

442
00:20:55,000 --> 00:20:55,730
I had no idea.

443
00:20:56,030 --> 00:20:57,160
Absolutely no idea.

444
00:20:57,750 --> 00:20:58,480
Our Leilei

445
00:20:58,480 --> 00:21:00,410
had always been an honest girl.

446
00:21:00,510 --> 00:21:03,510
She couldn't possibly have done
something like this!

447
00:21:03,720 --> 00:21:04,850
That's impossible.

448
00:21:05,720 --> 00:21:07,650
Leilei wasn't that kind of person.

449
00:21:08,590 --> 00:21:10,790
We've obtained the relevant evidence.

450
00:21:13,070 --> 00:21:15,800
Did you family members
really not know anything?

451
00:21:16,750 --> 00:21:18,640
Jian Leilei's call records show

452
00:21:18,960 --> 00:21:20,420
that for over a month,

453
00:21:20,590 --> 00:21:22,920
she hasn't been in contact
with this Xia Yi

454
00:21:23,200 --> 00:21:24,200
that you mentioned.

455
00:21:24,200 --> 00:21:25,920
No contact for over a month?

456
00:21:27,200 --> 00:21:30,200
None of the phone numbers
in Jian Leilei's call records

457
00:21:30,200 --> 00:21:32,110
belong to anyone named Xia Yi.

458
00:21:33,030 --> 00:21:33,680
Besides,

459
00:21:34,400 --> 00:21:36,000
in the trunk of Jian Leilei's car,

460
00:21:36,000 --> 00:21:37,930
we found a box full of luxury goods—

461
00:21:38,920 --> 00:21:39,980
roughly estimated

462
00:21:40,400 --> 00:21:42,240
to be worth nearly a million yuan.

463
00:21:42,240 --> 00:21:44,700
Only her fingerprints
were found on the box.

464
00:21:46,440 --> 00:21:47,110
Do you

465
00:21:47,960 --> 00:21:49,480
really know Jian Leilei?

466
00:21:53,140 --> 00:21:55,700
[Lihai Commercial Bank]

467
00:21:59,320 --> 00:22:00,490
Jian, still working?

468
00:21:59,700 --> 00:22:01,260
[Lihai Commercial Bank]

469
00:22:00,790 --> 00:22:01,560
I was about to leave.

470
00:22:01,560 --> 00:22:05,070
[Lihai Commercial Bank]

471
00:22:02,000 --> 00:22:02,600
Oh, right.

472
00:22:02,680 --> 00:22:03,790
Tomorrow at 10 AM,

473
00:22:03,810 --> 00:22:06,210
don't forget the meeting with that client.

474
00:22:06,270 --> 00:22:07,640
Okay, don't worry.

475
00:22:24,840 --> 00:22:32,680
[Leilei]

476
00:22:32,790 --> 00:22:36,040
[Missed Call]

477
00:22:37,960 --> 00:22:38,680
Why?

478
00:22:40,590 --> 00:22:42,750
Why did I miss your call?

479
00:22:43,500 --> 00:22:46,040
[Calls]

480
00:22:46,310 --> 00:22:48,070
Why did I fail to save you?

481
00:22:52,320 --> 00:22:52,880
Leilei.

482
00:22:56,510 --> 00:22:57,400
You're gone.

483
00:23:00,310 --> 00:23:01,640
What am I supposed to do?

484
00:23:15,770 --> 00:23:18,570
[Radiotherapy Department]

485
00:23:17,930 --> 00:23:19,590
Folks, who can relate?

486
00:23:19,590 --> 00:23:21,640
A college professor has turned into
a demon to torture her student.

487
00:23:21,640 --> 00:23:22,830
Come at me!

488
00:23:22,830 --> 00:23:23,640
I'm the demon!

489
00:23:23,640 --> 00:23:24,310
Come at me!

490
00:23:24,310 --> 00:23:25,590
Bring it on!

491
00:23:25,590 --> 00:23:26,240
I'm the demon!

492
00:23:26,240 --> 00:23:26,840
Come at me!

493
00:23:30,980 --> 00:23:31,750
Do you think it was easy for us

494
00:23:31,750 --> 00:23:34,880
to work ourselves to death
to support a college student?

495
00:23:34,960 --> 00:23:36,290
Now you won't let her graduate,

496
00:23:36,290 --> 00:23:37,240
and you've even driven her crazy.

497
00:23:37,240 --> 00:23:38,920
Are you trying to shirk responsibility?

498
00:23:38,920 --> 00:23:39,810
I admit that

499
00:23:39,880 --> 00:23:42,470
I didn't pay enough attention
to Li Changning's mental health.

500
00:23:42,470 --> 00:23:43,960
But her graduation thesis

501
00:23:44,270 --> 00:23:46,550
has a plagiarism rate of 40%.

502
00:23:46,750 --> 00:23:48,920
If I had given her
the thesis defense qualification,

503
00:23:48,920 --> 00:23:49,880
it would have been unfair

504
00:23:49,880 --> 00:23:51,750
to the students

505
00:23:51,790 --> 00:23:52,720
who worked seriously on their theses.

506
00:23:52,720 --> 00:23:55,440
I don't understand what you're
talking about, plague rate or something.

507
00:23:55,440 --> 00:23:56,310
You drove her crazy.

508
00:23:56,310 --> 00:23:57,510
You have to take responsibility for that!

509
00:23:57,510 --> 00:23:58,160
Calm down.

510
00:23:58,160 --> 00:24:00,240
Let's talk things out properly, alright?

511
00:24:00,240 --> 00:24:01,920
If we just give her a diploma like this,

512
00:24:01,920 --> 00:24:03,780
I believe when she recovers,

513
00:24:03,960 --> 00:24:05,760
she'll feel ashamed of herself.

514
00:24:05,880 --> 00:24:07,960
What if she faces problems again
in the future?

515
00:24:07,960 --> 00:24:11,070
Will there always be someone
protecting her and giving in to her?

516
00:24:11,070 --> 00:24:12,670
How could you hit her?

517
00:24:12,750 --> 00:24:13,920
-What are you doing?
-We could talk things out.

518
00:24:13,920 --> 00:24:14,270
How could you resort to violence?

519
00:24:14,270 --> 00:24:15,330
This is a hospital,

520
00:24:15,400 --> 00:24:16,880
not a place for violence and aggression!

521
00:24:16,880 --> 00:24:17,720
Call security!

522
00:24:17,720 --> 00:24:18,440
Calm down.

523
00:24:18,440 --> 00:24:20,720
-Look what happened to our daughter...
-Calm down.

524
00:24:20,720 --> 00:24:21,380
Pay up!

525
00:24:21,410 --> 00:24:22,470
Compensate me now!

526
00:24:23,090 --> 00:24:23,550
Ms. Yan.

527
00:24:23,550 --> 00:24:24,790
You drove her crazy.

528
00:24:24,790 --> 00:24:25,590
You have to pay with your life!

529
00:24:25,590 --> 00:24:26,450
That's enough!

530
00:24:26,480 --> 00:24:27,360
Let's go.

531
00:24:27,790 --> 00:24:28,910
Look at my child!

532
00:24:28,960 --> 00:24:30,090
Don't use violence.

533
00:24:30,510 --> 00:24:31,110
Pay up now!

534
00:24:31,880 --> 00:24:32,470
Director Lin.

535
00:24:32,470 --> 00:24:33,400
Regarding the diploma,

536
00:24:33,400 --> 00:24:34,070
you need to resolve it for us.

537
00:24:34,070 --> 00:24:35,130
Listen to me, okay?

538
00:24:51,560 --> 00:24:52,490
Are you alright?

539
00:24:53,050 --> 00:24:53,660
I'm okay.

540
00:24:59,420 --> 00:25:00,070
Thank you.

541
00:25:07,440 --> 00:25:08,440
Put some ice on it.

542
00:25:08,590 --> 00:25:09,790
Your face is swollen.

543
00:25:10,080 --> 00:25:11,150
No need. Thank you.

544
00:25:11,350 --> 00:25:13,010
I specially bought it for you.

545
00:25:14,240 --> 00:25:15,500
Can you give me my keys?

546
00:25:15,640 --> 00:25:17,650
Your emotional state
isn't suitable for driving.

547
00:25:17,650 --> 00:25:18,450
It's not safe.

548
00:25:18,640 --> 00:25:19,500
Where are you going?

549
00:25:19,500 --> 00:25:20,270
If it's on the way,

550
00:25:20,270 --> 00:25:20,920
since I just got off work,

551
00:25:20,920 --> 00:25:21,960
I can give you a ride.

552
00:25:21,960 --> 00:25:22,550
I don't want to trouble you.

553
00:25:22,550 --> 00:25:23,430
I can manage.

554
00:25:23,570 --> 00:25:24,370
No, you can't.

555
00:25:26,510 --> 00:25:27,640
It's too dangerous.

556
00:25:28,290 --> 00:25:30,150
This ear might have been injured.

557
00:25:30,440 --> 00:25:32,900
It could affect your balance
while driving.

558
00:25:33,370 --> 00:25:34,910
Even if you don't consider yourself,

559
00:25:34,910 --> 00:25:37,510
you should think about
innocent pedestrians.

560
00:25:41,110 --> 00:25:42,240
Where are you going?

561
00:25:44,440 --> 00:25:46,840
To the seafood restaurant on Shunbai Road.

562
00:25:51,030 --> 00:25:52,030
It's not on my way.

563
00:25:53,440 --> 00:25:55,480
But I've called a designated driver
for you.

564
00:25:55,480 --> 00:25:56,030
Thanks.

565
00:25:59,790 --> 00:26:00,680
I appreciate that,

566
00:26:00,680 --> 00:26:02,030
but I think adding you on WeChat is...

567
00:26:02,030 --> 00:26:03,160
You'll have to pay me

568
00:26:03,920 --> 00:26:05,180
for the driver, right?

569
00:26:07,860 --> 00:26:08,840
I'm sorry.

570
00:26:10,000 --> 00:26:10,780
I'm sorry.

571
00:26:24,350 --> 00:26:24,960
Ling.

572
00:26:27,240 --> 00:26:28,440
Isn't this restaurant expensive?

573
00:26:28,440 --> 00:26:29,790
This is Xia Yi's friend's restaurant.

574
00:26:29,790 --> 00:26:31,150
The decor looks so nice.

575
00:26:31,880 --> 00:26:33,070
Getting married?

576
00:26:33,350 --> 00:26:35,590
You've only known each other
for a few months.

577
00:26:35,590 --> 00:26:36,920
Isn't that a bit too fast?

578
00:26:36,920 --> 00:26:37,920
It's not.

579
00:26:37,920 --> 00:26:39,740
I know he's the one.

580
00:26:40,400 --> 00:26:41,590
How should I explain that feeling to you?

581
00:26:41,590 --> 00:26:42,790
He just gets me,

582
00:26:42,790 --> 00:26:45,400
and he genuinely appreciates me
from the bottom of his heart.

583
00:26:45,400 --> 00:26:47,590
Ms. Yan, I've finally met you.

584
00:26:47,920 --> 00:26:49,920
Leilei talks about you all the time.

585
00:26:49,960 --> 00:26:51,030
You're her idol.

586
00:26:51,960 --> 00:26:54,260
He's a maritime rescue volunteer.

587
00:26:54,350 --> 00:26:56,680
The first time we met,
he took me to the fish market.

588
00:26:56,680 --> 00:26:59,310
We saw a type of crab there.

589
00:26:59,310 --> 00:27:00,590
It looked like a flower crab,

590
00:27:00,590 --> 00:27:01,590
but it was actually highly poisonous.

591
00:27:01,590 --> 00:27:02,920
Eating it would land you
in intensive care.

592
00:27:02,920 --> 00:27:03,680
Xia Yi said

593
00:27:03,680 --> 00:27:05,680
this crab has a scientific name called...

594
00:27:05,680 --> 00:27:06,740
What's that again?

595
00:27:06,920 --> 00:27:08,200
Devil crab.

596
00:27:08,310 --> 00:27:10,370
Even more poisonous than jellyfish.

597
00:27:12,110 --> 00:27:12,590
Miss.

598
00:27:13,750 --> 00:27:15,640
Was something wrong with your meal?

599
00:27:15,640 --> 00:27:16,200
No.

600
00:27:16,470 --> 00:27:18,070
I'm here to look for someone.

601
00:27:19,000 --> 00:27:21,000
He often dines here,

602
00:27:21,020 --> 00:27:22,440
and he says he's a friend of yours.

603
00:27:22,440 --> 00:27:27,580
[Reservation: October 14—Ms. Jian]

604
00:27:23,200 --> 00:27:24,530
You mean Mr. Xia, right?

605
00:27:25,030 --> 00:27:26,400
He's a regular customer here,

606
00:27:26,400 --> 00:27:28,110
but he hasn't come here for a while.

607
00:27:27,600 --> 00:27:28,990
[Reservation: October 12—Ms. Jian]

608
00:27:29,510 --> 00:27:32,170
It was always Leilei
who made the reservations.

609
00:27:32,310 --> 00:27:33,550
Waiter, check please.

610
00:27:33,550 --> 00:27:34,160
Certainly.

611
00:27:34,160 --> 00:27:35,400
Sir, did you drive here?

612
00:27:35,400 --> 00:27:36,920
If we register your license plate,

613
00:27:36,920 --> 00:27:38,110
you can enjoy free parking.

614
00:27:38,110 --> 00:27:39,060
No need, thank you.

615
00:27:39,060 --> 00:27:39,440
Okay.

616
00:27:40,440 --> 00:27:41,000
Ms. Yan.

617
00:27:42,270 --> 00:27:43,470
I've finally met you.

618
00:27:43,490 --> 00:27:44,110
Sir.

619
00:27:44,790 --> 00:27:46,880
Could you please check the parking records

620
00:27:45,540 --> 00:27:47,420
[Reservation: October 18—Ms. Jian]

621
00:27:46,880 --> 00:27:49,280
for Miss Jian and her party
on October 18th?

622
00:27:49,550 --> 00:27:49,920
Sure.

623
00:27:49,920 --> 00:27:50,720
Just a moment.

624
00:27:51,640 --> 00:27:52,070
Hello,

625
00:27:52,070 --> 00:27:53,000
is this 114?

626
00:27:54,590 --> 00:27:56,590
Could you help me contact

627
00:27:56,590 --> 00:27:59,390
the owner of the car with license plate
Dong A 4728K

628
00:27:59,790 --> 00:28:02,160
and ask them to move their car
as soon as possible?

629
00:28:02,160 --> 00:28:02,560
No, no.

630
00:28:02,790 --> 00:28:03,750
It's like this.

631
00:28:04,070 --> 00:28:06,240
I accidentally scratched their car.

632
00:28:06,600 --> 00:28:08,350
I need to contact them directly

633
00:28:08,350 --> 00:28:10,680
to see how we should handle the insurance.

634
00:28:20,830 --> 00:28:21,480
Xia Yi.

635
00:28:26,400 --> 00:28:27,400
Car rental?

636
00:28:32,920 --> 00:28:34,430
Godmother, push me.

637
00:28:34,680 --> 00:28:35,950
Higher, Godmother.

638
00:28:36,110 --> 00:28:37,270
A little higher.

639
00:28:40,240 --> 00:28:40,980
Higher...

640
00:28:41,750 --> 00:28:42,820
[Sometimes kids' fun is really simple.]

641
00:28:51,050 --> 00:28:53,130
[My son says his godmother's
beef pies are the best in the world.]

642
00:28:56,420 --> 00:28:57,390
[You're a year older. In the new year,]

643
00:28:57,410 --> 00:28:58,790
[let's level up
and fight the monsters together.]

644
00:29:02,370 --> 00:29:02,600
[Godmother's exact words: "If you see the bear,
it's like seeing me—if the bear's here, I'm here."]

645
00:29:02,630 --> 00:29:03,040
[She really doesn't mind
how small our living room is.]

646
00:29:03,070 --> 00:29:05,420
["Memories" Music Festival]

647
00:29:05,440 --> 00:29:06,360
[has been accompanying Leilei and me for
countless days and nights.]

648
00:29:06,380 --> 00:29:07,350
[We're finally going to hear it live.]

649
00:29:07,380 --> 00:29:08,390
[Tonight, let's stay up
all night together.]

650
00:29:16,480 --> 00:29:18,800
♪ It's like a dream ♪

651
00:29:19,680 --> 00:29:22,620
♪ Our encounter was so fleeting ♪

652
00:29:23,890 --> 00:29:25,320
♪ You came like a spring breeze ♪

653
00:29:25,600 --> 00:29:30,130
♪ Softly blowing into my heart ♪

654
00:29:31,450 --> 00:29:37,930
♪ Where has your smile gone? ♪

655
00:29:38,910 --> 00:29:44,460
♪ That familiar smile I remember so well ♪

656
00:29:42,210 --> 00:29:46,210
[Lihai Renxin Hospital]

657
00:29:49,960 --> 00:29:51,410
Bed 23, Li Changning.

658
00:29:58,000 --> 00:29:59,860
Here, take this before you sleep.

659
00:30:27,640 --> 00:30:30,590
Changning used to live in the dormitory.

660
00:30:30,640 --> 00:30:33,570
She only moved out
at the beginning of this semester.

661
00:30:33,960 --> 00:30:34,920
Moved out?

662
00:30:35,960 --> 00:30:37,200
Does she live alone?

663
00:30:40,280 --> 00:30:42,680
The rent near the school
isn't cheap, is it?

664
00:30:44,720 --> 00:30:46,160
W-We're not really sure.

665
00:30:46,580 --> 00:30:48,370
She doesn't seem short of money.

666
00:30:48,370 --> 00:30:50,300
She bought the latest phone model,

667
00:30:50,510 --> 00:30:52,840
saying it was a birthday gift
for a friend.

668
00:30:53,480 --> 00:30:54,160
A friend?

669
00:30:55,160 --> 00:30:56,030
Her boyfriend?

670
00:30:57,490 --> 00:30:58,400
No idea.

671
00:31:02,030 --> 00:31:02,480
Hello?

672
00:31:02,680 --> 00:31:03,260
Uncle.

673
00:31:09,240 --> 00:31:10,100
Please come in.

674
00:31:15,790 --> 00:31:16,270
Ms. Yan.

675
00:31:21,960 --> 00:31:24,690
I was on an island in Minzhou

676
00:31:25,270 --> 00:31:28,320
attending a closed
marine search and rescue training camp.

677
00:31:28,320 --> 00:31:29,120
I only saw

678
00:31:29,830 --> 00:31:30,890
the dozens of calls

679
00:31:31,410 --> 00:31:32,350
Uncle and the police made to me

680
00:31:32,350 --> 00:31:33,750
after I got back.

681
00:31:36,480 --> 00:31:37,740
What exactly happened

682
00:31:38,680 --> 00:31:40,010
between you and Leilei?

683
00:31:42,880 --> 00:31:43,920
About a month ago,

684
00:31:45,750 --> 00:31:47,030
we had a big fight.

685
00:31:47,820 --> 00:31:49,280
You want another 500,000?

686
00:31:50,560 --> 00:31:53,160
If it's not convenient,
less would be fine too.

687
00:31:53,480 --> 00:31:55,880
It's that cryptocurrency again, isn't it?

688
00:31:55,880 --> 00:31:58,140
We've already lost a lot of money on that.

689
00:31:58,640 --> 00:32:00,680
We can't keep pouring money
into it endlessly.

690
00:32:00,680 --> 00:32:01,480
You mean

691
00:32:02,270 --> 00:32:05,530
Leilei had already borrowed money
from you several times?

692
00:32:06,880 --> 00:32:07,480
Yes.

693
00:32:08,880 --> 00:32:10,160
Just now, Xia

694
00:32:10,720 --> 00:32:11,690
showed me

695
00:32:12,030 --> 00:32:13,830
his transfer records to Leilei.

696
00:32:13,830 --> 00:32:15,240
It started with 10,000 or 20,000,

697
00:32:15,240 --> 00:32:16,910
but then it kept increasing,

698
00:32:17,240 --> 00:32:20,070
to 50,000, 80,000, and even 100,000.

699
00:32:21,480 --> 00:32:23,480
Your family runs a big business.

700
00:32:23,480 --> 00:32:24,680
The little money I make

701
00:32:24,680 --> 00:32:26,240
certainly isn't impressive to you,

702
00:32:26,240 --> 00:32:28,140
but you don't have to look down on me,
right?

703
00:32:28,140 --> 00:32:29,000
How could you think that?

704
00:32:29,000 --> 00:32:31,660
It's your attitude
that makes me think this way.

705
00:32:31,920 --> 00:32:32,680
Xia Yi.

706
00:32:32,680 --> 00:32:34,960
I, Jian Leilei, don't depend on any man.

707
00:32:35,000 --> 00:32:36,480
If you think I'm only after your money,

708
00:32:36,480 --> 00:32:38,010
get out of my life right now!

709
00:32:38,880 --> 00:32:39,680
Leilei and I

710
00:32:40,480 --> 00:32:41,940
were about to get married.

711
00:32:42,070 --> 00:32:43,230
Actually, for me,

712
00:32:43,440 --> 00:32:45,300
it really wasn't about the money.

713
00:32:46,680 --> 00:32:48,480
The main problem was that Leilei

714
00:32:48,880 --> 00:32:50,310
had really gone too far.

715
00:32:51,240 --> 00:32:53,830
I originally thought
that while I was away,

716
00:32:54,110 --> 00:32:55,270
we could separate temporarily

717
00:32:55,270 --> 00:32:56,680
and both cool down a bit.

718
00:32:56,740 --> 00:32:57,510
If I had known
things would end up like this,

719
00:32:57,510 --> 00:32:59,570
I should have just lent her the money.

720
00:32:59,880 --> 00:33:00,620
Xia.

721
00:33:01,640 --> 00:33:03,920
As for the money
you transferred to Leilei,

722
00:33:03,920 --> 00:33:06,520
my wife and I will definitely
pay you back.

723
00:33:06,620 --> 00:33:07,350
No, Uncle,

724
00:33:08,270 --> 00:33:09,600
that's not what I meant.

725
00:33:10,660 --> 00:33:12,340
When Leilei was with you,

726
00:33:13,030 --> 00:33:14,690
did she ever use luxury goods?

727
00:33:15,350 --> 00:33:16,080
Yes, she did.

728
00:33:16,680 --> 00:33:18,750
Then why have I never seen them?

729
00:33:21,480 --> 00:33:23,400
Maybe she didn't want you to know.

730
00:33:25,590 --> 00:33:26,400
Do you

731
00:33:27,200 --> 00:33:28,880
really know Jian Leilei?

732
00:33:31,480 --> 00:33:31,880
Uncle.

733
00:33:33,200 --> 00:33:35,680
I hope you and Auntie
can take care of yourselves.

734
00:33:35,680 --> 00:33:36,680
My condolences.

735
00:33:39,310 --> 00:33:40,510
If you need anything,

736
00:33:41,070 --> 00:33:42,270
call me anytime.

737
00:33:45,750 --> 00:33:46,350
Thank you.

738
00:33:47,440 --> 00:33:48,040
Thank you.

739
00:33:50,570 --> 00:33:52,210
I need to get back to the hospital.

740
00:33:52,210 --> 00:33:53,540
My wife will be worried.

741
00:33:59,310 --> 00:34:01,110
Ms. Yan, I'll be going now too.

742
00:34:02,510 --> 00:34:03,030
Xia Yi.

743
00:34:05,880 --> 00:34:07,210
Can we talk for a moment?

744
00:34:10,630 --> 00:34:12,159
Why isn't your phone number

745
00:34:12,550 --> 00:34:13,760
under your name?

746
00:34:14,230 --> 00:34:15,960
Uncle just asked me about that.

747
00:34:16,590 --> 00:34:19,190
Our company set up a corporate plan
for all employees.

748
00:34:19,190 --> 00:34:21,190
The accountant gave me this SIM card,

749
00:34:21,190 --> 00:34:23,050
and I've been using it ever since.

750
00:34:23,710 --> 00:34:25,040
And what about your car?

751
00:34:25,440 --> 00:34:27,639
For business convenience, our company

752
00:34:27,760 --> 00:34:28,400
rented a Range Rover SUV

753
00:34:28,400 --> 00:34:30,110
for me here.

754
00:34:30,590 --> 00:34:32,250
Leilei loved driving around.

755
00:34:33,000 --> 00:34:33,840
You know that.

756
00:34:35,150 --> 00:34:37,150
Actually, I've already explained all this

757
00:34:37,150 --> 00:34:38,940
to Officer Li.

758
00:34:40,760 --> 00:34:41,400
Is that so?

759
00:34:49,699 --> 00:34:50,760
Hello, Officer Li.

760
00:34:51,400 --> 00:34:52,280
This is Xia Yi.

761
00:34:54,110 --> 00:34:54,570
Yes.

762
00:34:55,190 --> 00:34:57,120
I've already met Leilei's family.

763
00:34:58,400 --> 00:35:00,000
I've explained everything.

764
00:35:02,290 --> 00:35:04,420
Okay, thank you, Officer Li. Goodbye.

765
00:35:08,110 --> 00:35:08,630
Ms. Yan.

766
00:35:09,800 --> 00:35:10,930
I know you're upset.

767
00:35:11,550 --> 00:35:12,840
If you feel that

768
00:35:13,190 --> 00:35:14,070
yelling at me

769
00:35:14,070 --> 00:35:15,600
would make you feel better,

770
00:35:16,840 --> 00:35:17,760
I can take it.

771
00:35:18,800 --> 00:35:21,460
It might make me
feel a little better myself too.

772
00:35:39,140 --> 00:35:41,850
[Lihai Renxin Hospital]

773
00:35:44,480 --> 00:35:46,190
This patient has developed
some drug resistance.

774
00:35:46,190 --> 00:35:47,520
We might need to do MECT.

775
00:35:47,630 --> 00:35:49,800
But his family
is quite resistant to electrotherapy.

776
00:35:49,800 --> 00:35:51,400
It's okay. I'll talk to them.

777
00:35:51,630 --> 00:35:53,000
Help me remind the attending physician

778
00:35:53,000 --> 00:35:54,710
to reduce the Chlorpromazine dosage.

779
00:35:54,710 --> 00:35:56,920
It does affect the cardiovascular system
to some extent.

780
00:35:56,920 --> 00:35:57,280
Okay.

781
00:36:16,950 --> 00:36:18,000
[Lihai University of Finance and Economics]

782
00:36:20,360 --> 00:36:20,930
Feng.

783
00:36:21,070 --> 00:36:21,750
Feng.

784
00:36:22,920 --> 00:36:23,590
Where's Feng?

785
00:36:23,590 --> 00:36:24,550
Do you know where Feng is?

786
00:36:24,550 --> 00:36:25,000
Where's Feng?

787
00:36:25,000 --> 00:36:25,730
I don't know.

788
00:36:27,550 --> 00:36:28,800
Do you know where Feng is?

789
00:36:28,800 --> 00:36:29,440
Where's Feng?

790
00:36:29,440 --> 00:36:32,840
-What Feng? From which department?
-Why ask if you don't know him?

791
00:36:32,840 --> 00:36:33,740
Are you crazy?

792
00:36:34,190 --> 00:36:34,950
Feng.

793
00:36:48,600 --> 00:36:50,600
I can die for you too!

794
00:36:50,630 --> 00:36:51,510
Feng!

795
00:36:52,140 --> 00:36:54,570
I can die for you too!

796
00:36:58,070 --> 00:36:59,400
I'm sorry, Teacher.

797
00:36:58,130 --> 00:37:01,430
[Lihai Renxin Hospital
Medical Case Records]

798
00:36:59,630 --> 00:37:01,190
I came to visit Changning today,

799
00:37:01,190 --> 00:37:02,230
and she kept begging me,

800
00:37:02,230 --> 00:37:02,760
saying

801
00:37:02,880 --> 00:37:04,360
she'd just go out for a while.

802
00:37:04,360 --> 00:37:06,890
And she said
there was nothing wrong with her.

803
00:37:06,920 --> 00:37:09,840
She was just pretending
to get her diploma

804
00:37:09,840 --> 00:37:11,040
and scare the school.

805
00:37:13,230 --> 00:37:15,200
Who is this "Feng" guy anyway?

806
00:37:16,360 --> 00:37:18,170
He's Changning's boyfriend.

807
00:37:18,280 --> 00:37:19,450
His name is Xu Feng.

808
00:37:19,880 --> 00:37:22,320
He's from
the University of Finance and Economics.

809
00:37:22,320 --> 00:37:23,510
But it seems

810
00:37:23,510 --> 00:37:26,170
they've been talking about
breaking up lately.

811
00:37:26,800 --> 00:37:29,110
You didn't report such a serious matter
to the school?

812
00:37:29,110 --> 00:37:30,360
Do you think you're helping her?

813
00:37:30,360 --> 00:37:31,590
You're hurting her.

814
00:37:32,510 --> 00:37:35,070
I've always told you
there's no use in girls getting educated.

815
00:37:35,070 --> 00:37:36,800
Now she's fooling around with some boy

816
00:37:36,800 --> 00:37:38,460
and making herself act crazy.

817
00:37:38,920 --> 00:37:39,590
How embarrassing!

818
00:37:39,590 --> 00:37:40,150
Keep it down.

819
00:37:40,150 --> 00:37:41,810
Take your hands off me! Let go!

820
00:37:45,760 --> 00:37:46,690
What's going on?

821
00:37:48,070 --> 00:37:48,730
Yan Ling,

822
00:37:48,920 --> 00:37:50,320
your name's been cleared.

823
00:37:50,320 --> 00:37:50,920
Li Changning

824
00:37:50,920 --> 00:37:52,050
is completely fine.

825
00:37:53,670 --> 00:37:56,070
Dr. Luo, what's going on with
Li Changning?

826
00:37:56,360 --> 00:37:58,050
She's in an acute stress state right now.

827
00:37:58,050 --> 00:37:59,980
We can't fully trust what she says.

828
00:38:00,150 --> 00:38:01,410
Excuse me, let me through.

829
00:38:01,410 --> 00:38:02,240
Dr. Luo,

830
00:38:02,920 --> 00:38:03,920
let me take a look.

831
00:38:03,960 --> 00:38:05,190
How are you injured so badly?

832
00:38:05,190 --> 00:38:05,840
There's no need for this.

833
00:38:05,840 --> 00:38:06,440
Tian Tian,

834
00:38:07,030 --> 00:38:08,630
please step outside for now.

835
00:38:13,510 --> 00:38:15,310
Based on the latest assessment,

836
00:38:15,360 --> 00:38:16,550
the real source of stress

837
00:38:16,550 --> 00:38:18,670
comes from Li Changning's
emotional relationships.

838
00:38:18,670 --> 00:38:20,130
Not being able to graduate

839
00:38:20,320 --> 00:38:22,580
was at most the last straw that broke her.

840
00:38:26,440 --> 00:38:28,550
You should at least
apologize to Ms. Yan.

841
00:38:28,550 --> 00:38:29,360
Changning's father,

842
00:38:29,360 --> 00:38:31,760
we could hold you responsible for assault.

843
00:38:32,430 --> 00:38:33,490
No need, it's okay.

844
00:38:36,360 --> 00:38:37,360
I have a child too.

845
00:38:38,240 --> 00:38:40,480
I understand how you felt at that moment.

846
00:38:40,480 --> 00:38:42,880
I'm sorry.

847
00:38:43,110 --> 00:38:45,920
She was actually a very obedient child
when she was little.

848
00:38:45,920 --> 00:38:47,070
Who'd have expected...

849
00:38:47,070 --> 00:38:49,440
Who'd have expected
that she would lie to us?

850
00:38:49,440 --> 00:38:50,900
The most urgent matter now

851
00:38:51,550 --> 00:38:53,510
is to get Changning proper treatment.

852
00:38:53,510 --> 00:38:55,910
As long as
she takes her studies seriously,

853
00:38:56,070 --> 00:38:57,130
once she recovers,

854
00:38:59,030 --> 00:39:01,690
I'll help her apply for
a graduation extension.

855
00:39:03,000 --> 00:39:05,060
Helping Changning go on with her life

856
00:39:05,070 --> 00:39:06,880
is more important than anything else.

857
00:39:06,880 --> 00:39:08,670
Thank you, Ms. Yan. Thank you.

858
00:39:20,510 --> 00:39:21,190
Yan Ling.

859
00:39:21,920 --> 00:39:24,260
The police said
the case is already closed.

860
00:39:24,260 --> 00:39:25,520
We can go pick up Leilei

861
00:39:25,590 --> 00:39:26,880
tomorrow.

862
00:39:27,440 --> 00:39:27,960
They said

863
00:39:27,960 --> 00:39:30,220
that even if there's a criminal suspect,

864
00:39:30,630 --> 00:39:32,300
according to national law,

865
00:39:32,800 --> 00:39:34,880
no criminal responsibility is pursued

866
00:39:34,880 --> 00:39:36,880
if the suspect is already deceased.

867
00:39:40,030 --> 00:39:40,940
I've decided—

868
00:39:41,000 --> 00:39:42,590
I'll choose tulips for my bouquet.

869
00:39:42,590 --> 00:39:43,900
Make sure you catch it.

870
00:40:16,970 --> 00:40:21,550
[Morgue]

871
00:40:25,300 --> 00:40:26,960
You can give the clothes to me.

872
00:40:31,150 --> 00:40:32,510
Our Leilei...

873
00:40:33,630 --> 00:40:34,590
Our Leilei

874
00:40:34,590 --> 00:40:37,360
died unmarried.

875
00:40:37,960 --> 00:40:38,790
Let me

876
00:40:39,550 --> 00:40:41,000
change her clothes.

877
00:40:43,670 --> 00:40:44,110
I...

878
00:40:44,110 --> 00:40:46,400
With your health condition,
I don't think it's a good idea.

879
00:40:46,400 --> 00:40:47,630
Given how emotional you are,

880
00:40:47,630 --> 00:40:48,970
if something happens,

881
00:40:49,070 --> 00:40:51,600
we won't be able to
take that responsibility.

882
00:40:54,980 --> 00:40:55,630
Auntie.

883
00:40:56,630 --> 00:40:57,630
Let me handle this.

884
00:40:57,630 --> 00:40:59,550
I'll go. Don't worry.

885
00:41:09,960 --> 00:41:10,490
This way.

886
00:41:14,470 --> 00:41:15,430
[Morgue]

887
00:41:16,440 --> 00:41:18,150
I want to see her one more time!

888
00:41:18,510 --> 00:41:28,390
I want to see my daughter one more time!

889
00:43:22,050 --> 00:43:25,720
[The Dark Romance]

890
00:43:57,230 --> 00:43:58,000
Bed 32.

891
00:43:58,000 --> 00:43:58,670
Tomorrow morning,

892
00:43:58,670 --> 00:44:00,320
schedule a neurosurgery consultation
for him.

893
00:44:00,320 --> 00:44:01,580
Make a note of it for me.

894
00:44:12,640 --> 00:44:13,360
Keep an eye on her!

895
00:44:13,360 --> 00:44:14,590
Li Changning, calm down!
